h unemployed youth. In case you have completed your education and are not getting a job, then Bihar state govt. will provide you with Rs. 1000 as monthly allowance. In the Bihar Budget 2018, the state govt. has allocated Rs. 60,000 crore for this mega unemployment allowance scheme. Bihar Berojgari Bhatta 2019 has the main objective to provide assistance to jobless youths who does not possess any permanent income source.1. Bihar Berojgari Bhatta Online Registration 2018-2019"}